        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install fan hub assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>The standard fan hub assembly is serviced as a unit. The assembly is made up of the following non
                    serviceable items:
                </para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>Fan and pulley mounting hub</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>Fan bearing hub</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>Bearing assembly</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>M10 x 70 bolt</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>Fan bearing retainer</para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f2650655.5" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figH05/H05030.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the fan drive mounting bolts (typical)</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the hex flange bolts required and tighten to the standard torque value , unless
                otherwise noted .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650656" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figh05/H05027.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="448px"/>
